title: CPUT student voted “The coolest girl in Cape Town” (Cape Peninsula University of Technology)
text: ( Source : Cape Peninsula University of Technology ) First-year CPUT film and video production student Tony Gum has recently been dubbed 'the coolest girl in Cape Town ' by one of the most influential style bibles in the world, Vogue Magazine .
